OL,5, TV chef James Martin has been asked to 
OL,6, change his behaviour at work after ITV 
OL,7, received complaints about his treatment
OL,8, of production staff.                   
OL,10,FConcerns were raised during the recent 
OL,11,Ffilming of James Martin's Spanish      
OL,12,FAdventure, his latest travel cooking   
OL,13,Fshow.                                  
OL,15,FIn a joint statement, Martin and       
OL,16,Fproduction company Blue Marlin said    
OL,17,Fthey "agree lessons have been learned".
OL,19,FAn ITV spokesman said "people and their
OL,20,Fwelfare" was their "highest priority". 
